entries.journal_entry_description: The Corellian Times Reporter asked you to speak with a friend of hers who was having some trouble. You've agreed to see what you can do.
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: Sheelya has lost her house keys to some thugs. Her description seems to match the description of some of Greck's thugs. There's an old powerplant that they hang out near. You should go there and see if you can find them and get Sheelya's keys.
entries.task01_message_box_text: Greck's thug had an remote explosive device! After examining it you're certain that they must have planted explosives elsewhere. Beat down Greck's men until one of them tells you where you can find the rest of the explosives.
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: Greck's thugs have planted bombs in more locations. Take them down until you find out where all the bombs are.
entries.task03_message_box_text: One of Greck's men cracked just before he died. You know now the general locations of the four bombs they planted. Go disarm them.
entries.task04_journal_entry_description: Find and disarm all the bombs that Greck's men planted in the area.
